{"tid":1745223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選唔係只係贏一啖氣，係要贏資源，贏權力","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T16:25:52.000Z","uid":269287,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"1cde3233da8206372c3618079c8e3d1d54216e3d","tid":1745223,"uid":269287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:10:30.000Z","msg":"千萬唔好覺得區選無用<br />\n<br />\n1) 每人每年100萬的資源, 扣左人工後, 好多係津貼, 你請個判過監o既手足就可以用呢筆錢請<br />\n你要培養新人都要有錢請佢做議員助理先得架, 唔通要義士日日做義工咩<br />\n2) 每區每年1億社區建設及文娛活動的經費, 你估民建聯係阿爺比錢派米? 好多時係係區議會申請項目撥款借花敬佛，錢政府出名就我攞, 你o個區過半泛民做到主席, o的錢你想點派都得, 淺藍真係要靠派蛇齋餅糉收買<br />\n3) 互選1位立法會議員, 民主派過半就攞到<br />\n4) 互選117位特首選委, 如果攞到到時泛民+商界絕對可以控制過半選委, 選邊個做特首就有話語權(CY都係689票當選, 你話無左呢117鐵票會點真係無人知)<br />\n5)區議會由民選產生, 如果全部區議會由民主派過半, 咁日後政府出賣市民, 十八區區議會就可以打住民意聯合讉責兼處處不合作, 等政府管治成本增加, 淨係趕O的藍屍大媽出區議會已經大快人心啦<br />\n<br />\n重點係, 呢O的資源同權力你唔爭, 就係送晒比班保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n11月24日, 一投都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e11b4e95eee039acc69c1818c5da4a79b21fda","tid":1745223,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"bb1fe7ed38ac5a2d34a4e60fb18a2eaf73162053","tid":1745223,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1e11b4e95eee039acc69c1818c5da4a79b21fda","tid":1745223,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"同意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>所以麻煩連登以外幫手文宣，以下正皮、加推、幫手做，時間無多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出街全部對家街站，死得啦，麻煩認真幫推呢個整合左既行動PO啦，再唔做的野輸死喇：</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【行動post】《緊急》全民選舉文宣+鍵盤戰</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743618</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>原PO<br />\n選舉文宣！文宣！文宣呀！唔夠對家多呀！的牆無曬喇！</ins></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezmgyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezmgyS</a>"},{"pid":"82175c57643c5b3ddc65e0416fb3b57627ac0c9e","tid":1745223,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"點解可以無人推"},{"pid":"547d423681a4fffd05db93579359c4df27791628","tid":1745223,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"345f377895cb002bd5581f89eebc87bc6f9a3ab1","tid":1745223,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:40:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c1558bfca16c8875c55628aacced147fedb559f2","tid":1745223,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:40:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"215722aa43f4e3ca14c670670c927a915ab5aa5f","tid":1745223,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a78e18fa65998d93177c3c8b5bcfa8fbcef80d7b","tid":1745223,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d262779c2d9fbf5c8aa16cee4982883c1e0ba66f","tid":1745223,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"52db4c2b7103ece51b80db931b233367cf817147","tid":1745223,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9728a766e829aadb9d15c7f3d7cbc03822aa5f6","tid":1745223,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:4