"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42da83bf621527c592a10cf6cd65ed5d86be81b9","tid":1745223,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d57f92f127cab77e1676d9700b2e3f0afcb70c","tid":1745223,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:41:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78f8282c319fdae0937874ca101a55d295db7755","tid":1745223,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n收到風建制除左&quot;時間&quot;(呢2日吹到行既愈早投票愈好)仲有2招蠱惑野<br />\n<br />\n1) 搵啲揸拐扙老藍絲響去票站既樓梯/電梯頂住大家(有唔少票站得一條路去的)<br />\n博大家唔敢打人<br />\n解決方法<br />\na) 搵番老黃絲頂番住佢地,男頂男,女頂女<br />\nb) 後生巴絲她溫柔咁扶佢地快速行完條路,佢地一叫暈or唔舒服就夾手夾腳她溫柔咁抬佢走,又係男招呼男.女招呼女<br />\n<br />\n2) POPO講明會高調巡邏,收到風會每幾分鐘就埋去泛民街站查一次(佢真係有權咁做,好似一晚查酒吧4次牌咁)<br />\n解決方法<br />\n和理非最多係&quot;人&quot;,呢幾日去到區選,各區和理非可以組團去建制同偽黃侯選人街站,<br />\n用各種方式去令佢地全日唔得閒,e.g. 成團人全日車輪戰去同佢地傾同佢地拗,<br />\n但千萬唔好鬧,務求癱瘓建制同偽黃街站.記住,唔好一個人去,要成團咁去,<br />\n仲有,唔駛一團人做晒一日,和理非就係人多,幾團人磨佢一個街站都得<br />\n<br />\n區選唔好唔投,你點睇區選都好,只要係俾建制贏(只係贏就夠,唔駛大贏)<br />\n林鄭同POPO直頭可以大條道理出機關槍,所以一定要投,要正正經經咁投<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2919f7094cb20cd1060983e5de6abb1df7f6d771","tid":1745223,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:43:41.000Z","msg":"建制派啲地區主任，收緊兩三皮一個月<br />\n<br />\n當選唔使養倒返轉上撽兼請多幾個黨工<br />\n<br />\n仲可以掛個名籌旗<br />\n<br />\n落選啲穩陣費又要加大"},{"pid":"d020685f9fa9db8fac7bb0bc66f982725ff88574","tid":1745223,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4205b8d79f2ecce8e7828638bab364959a85a3f3","tid":1745223,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d94e34759ab9d47425a8c583586bde97aac88cfb","tid":1745223,"uid":41717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1d2da78bfb60089170e206eac45797644ad407","tid":1745223,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"淨係第1點都收左皮<br />\n<br />\n都無人肯應承會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"有冇候選人話會肯請義士做議員助理？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能我廢啦,未收到風/未見有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"泛民就算9數啦"},{"pid":"21b31aea3087948a5914c83e33f76af60fdaea90","tid":1745223,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d020685f9fa9db8fac7bb0bc66f982725ff88574","tid":1745223,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4205b8d79f2ecce8e7828638bab364959a85a3f3","tid":1745223,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d94e34759ab9d47425a8c583586bde97aac88cfb","tid":1745223,"uid":41717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"有冇候選人話會肯請義士做議員助理？"},"citedBy":1,"