<br />\n<br />\n11月24日, 一投都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"巴打好文, 配合翻合適既標題(舊嗰個標題真係趕客),<br />\n唔推唔得!!"},{"pid":"0507da1628c0cb80d32e9bf9d229685988446d1e","tid":1745223,"uid":229225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"我守承諾, 幫推 2/10<br />\n星期日投票!!"},{"pid":"8e0261cc3a75195d5f7d829c48b5ee26ac78c057","tid":1745223,"uid":229225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"我守承諾, 幫推 3/10<br />\n星期日投票!!"},{"pid":"02ae77bb9ce3230d08dd6f5c6b64f7aa698b15dc","tid":1745223,"uid":229225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"我守承諾, 幫推 4/10<br />\n星期日投票!!"},{"pid":"ad6cc6da65bcb6232dcf8561cb65f898074611c5","tid":1745223,"uid":331678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"原全同意"},{"pid":"7237ff9005d1450ddb02ea36a15677f84283d19a","tid":1745223,"uid":229225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"我守承諾, 幫推 5/10<br />\n星期日投票!!"},{"pid":"42333e9272a919dfa1a883a9e3ee52c0a370cf8e","tid":1745223,"uid":229225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"我守承諾, 幫推 6/10<br />\n星期日投票!!"},{"pid":"0cd10a279ecb3a841aeb61da148351afffa3669c","tid":1745223,"uid":229225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"我守承諾, 幫推 7/10<br />\n星期日投票!!"},{"pid":"ebb6ea66385c57a649974077e35dc82e6f223629","tid":1745223,"uid":251265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"企圖抹黑民主派，呼籲手足投白票一律視為共諜"}]}